mg_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741950/extras/5e20241d0ddd3a4b1a2b1f0df4232693.poster.avif?t=1769131129\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741950/extras/5e20241d0ddd3a4b1a2b1f0df4232693.webm?t=1769131129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741950/extras/5e20241d0ddd3a4b1a2b1f0df4232693.mp4?t=1769131129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Frostfall Park</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frostfall park is a romantic destination for some... but the start of a war for others. Navigate through this quiet outdoor park, checking every corner to make sure you're safe... Will you ride the Frostwheel, climb some wires, or maybe you'll hide in a maze. Unravel the story and learn about Amber's true past...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But thats not all...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every Christmas a new map (and more) will be released FOR FREE! Stay tuned!</strong></p>",
